  <h1>About Surya Engineering College</h1>
  <div class="content">
    <p><strong>Surya Engineering College</strong>, located in Erode, Tamil Nadu, is a premier institution affiliated with Anna University. Established with the vision of empowering rural and urban students alike, the college offers high-quality education in a wide range of engineering disciplines.</p>

    <p>Our mission is to nurture innovation, discipline, and research-based learning. We aim to provide holistic education that develops students both technically and ethically.</p>

    <p>We offer a vibrant campus with well-equipped labs, smart classrooms, experienced faculty, and a strong placement record across core and IT companies.</p>

    <p><strong>Why Choose Surya?</strong></p>
